#OPENmadrid. Open Architecture for the City. 24.06.2013 - 26.06.2013

Place: Medialab-Prado

#OPENmadrid is a meeting point and a space for reflection dedicated to new architectural practices for the city, seen through the lens of free culture and urban innovation.

It includes talks, panels and streaming sessions.

This event intends to become a referent for all those who believe in, work for, suffer for, enjoy and dream the city.


